title: make UNFI easier to understand
body:
there are many beginners in the crypto space right now. 
we can easily reach them with making it easier to understand.
create a youtube chanel from unifi itself with short video's on:
-how to earn UP
-what is staking 
-why can you stake
etc.

the video's must be short and powerfull

A video is much easier to understand than a white paper.
plus it binds the community more together to see the creator once in a time.
author: 0x0eE4be93F5E35eAb685D64ed8901522100F7Ec04
